---
title: Roasted Pork Tenderloin with Lemony Potato & Zucchini Hash
description: We love a crispy potato hash, but hate messy stovetop frying. In this recipe, we’re roasting the potatoes in the oven before tossing them into the skillet with zucchini. A touch of lemon takes this dish over the top!
